snippet.title: Keepsake County - Alpha 0.56 Now Available
snippet.description:
Keepsake County is a midwestern stealth game, where players burglarize procedurally generated farmhouses as fast as they can before the cops show up. The Neighbors is now Keepsake County! Play the latest alpha, available on itch.io! Sprawling rooms, tons of loot, new color palettes, loads of characters, and a world of interactivity.

Play it on Steam for Next Fest here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1162860/Keepsake_County/

Check out the alpha here:
https://forwardinstinct.itch.io/keepsake-county

Drop us some feedback or bugs here:
https://discord.gg/forwardinstinct
